overview: LatinTutor.net provides customized Latin tutoring online via voice and video chatting. Visitors to the site can use it for general information about topics related to Latin grammar and studying Latin, and can also email or call to book a Latin lesson. Latin lessons are tailored to meet student’s specifications and their needs for the course - no matter what text book is used or what goal is set. Latintutor.net provides personalized Latin tutoring to students who don’t have access to in-home tutoring, or who find that they learn better online.
